OL,3,CGeorge and Amal Clooney criticise 'war
OL,4,Con truth, journalists and women'
OL,6,FHuman rights lawyer Amal Clooney has
OL,7,Fcriticised an ongoing "war on truth
OL,8,Fand journalists", saying that "women
OL,9,Fand children increasingly on the front
OL,10,Flines".
OL,12,FThe barrister and her husband,
OL,13,FHollywood actor , spoke at the 2024
OL,14,FSkoll World Forum in Oxford about
OL,15,Ftheir work with the Clooney Foundation
OL,16,FFor Justice, which they co-founded and
OL,17,Fco-chair.
