OL,3,CGeorge and Amal Clooney criticise 'war
OL,4,Con truth, journalists and women'
OL,6,FAddressing the audience, Amal said:
OL,7,F"We're living through a time when we
OL,8,Fhave more violent conflicts than at
OL,9,Fany time since the Second World War."
OL,11,FShe added: "I also think there's a war
OL,12,Fon truth and truth-tellers and
OL,13,Fjournalists, and we need to fight
OL,14,Fagainst that as well."
OL,16,F"In too many places there's a war on
OL,17,Fwomen, and women are still fighting
OL,18,Fthe most basic battles for their
OL,19,Ffreedoms."
