OL,6,FShe later warned about a loss of
OL,7,Fwomen's rights and said: "We see
OL,8,Freversals in things like women's
OL,9,Frights, not just in Afghanistan, but
OL,10,Falso in places like the United States."
OL,12,FHer husband then interjected:
OL,13,F"Arizona, apparently."
OL,15,FThe US state has recently revived an
OL,16,F1864 law that criminalises abortion
OL,17,Fthroughout pregnancy unless a woman's
OL,18,Flife is at risk.
