OL,6,F"(The film) Good Night Good Luck I
OL,7,Fwrote because I was being called a
OL,8,Ftraitor to my country by my own
OL,9,Fcountry for being against the war in
OL,10,FIraq," he said.
OL,12,F"The idea was anybody who spoke
OL,13,Fagainst the war in 2003 was a traitor,
OL,14,Fand it wasn't really fun. They were
OL,15,Fpicketing my movies and all that kind
OL,16,Fof stuff."
