OL,6,FHe told the audience that storytelling
OL,7,Fis about "finding a way to relate to
OL,8,Fpeople things that they can understand
OL,9,Fand not overwhelm them with peas and
OL,10,Fcarrots."
OL,12,FDescribing what The Clooney Foundation
OL,13,FFor Justice does, Amal said: "All of
OL,14,Four programmes in one way or another,
OL,15,Fare attempting to meet some of these
OL,16,Fchallenges.
OL,18,F"And the way we do it is by providing
OL,19,Ffree legal support to victims of
OL,20,Fabuses of human rights.
