OL,6,F"So we have a lot still to do. But
OL,7,Fwe've had dozens of people freed
OL,8,Fbecause of interventions that we've
OL,9,Fmade in individual cases.
OL,11,F"We've also spent years sometimes
OL,12,Ftrying to track down war criminals and
OL,13,Fgather enough evidence against them to
OL,14,Ftrigger a prosecution.
OL,16,F"So none of this happens as quickly or
OL,17,Fas simply as it should. But I think I
OL,18,Fspeak for both of us when I say, and
OL,19,Feveryone at the foundation, when I say
OL,20,Fwe're as determined as ever to
OL,21,Fcontinue to do this work."
